headline: Influenza A(H1N1) - update 33
main_text: As of 06:00 GMT, 19 May 2009, 40 countries have officially reported 9830 cases of influenza A(H1N1) infection, including 79 deaths. The breakdown of the number of laboratory-confirmed cases by country is given in the following table and map.
